{
  "name": "RPlog_Addressing_the_OS_Paladin",
  "title": "Addressing the OS Paladin",
  "summary": "Aboard the New Republic station OS Paladin, the newly appointed Chief of State's aide, Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard, gathers the station's pilots, crew, and cadets in the main hangar bay for a morale-raising address. Speaking from a makeshift podium of cargo crates, she reaffirms the diplomatic branch's gratitude and solidarity with the military in the wake of recent plague-driven losses and Imperial gains. The cocky Cadet Jamta repeatedly interrupts to argue that Rogue Squadron should be reactivated and to volunteer himself as a temporary commander, drawing rebukes from the wheelchair-bound pilot Naota and quiet observation from the convalescing Cadet Jimmy Pickle. Captain Mora Rodriguez, watching from the back, finally silences the cadet by ordering him to file a report on insubordination before dismissing the assembly. Ambrosia closes with words of trust and sympathy, then hurries off to answer an urgent comlink message.",
